jp.ac.keio.bio.fun.xitosbml.util

Class ModelSaver

  • java.lang.Object
    • jp.ac.keio.bio.fun.xitosbml.util.ModelSaver

  • public class ModelSaver
extends Object
    The class ModelSaver, which is an utility class to save SBML document to a file. The saved SBML file will contain an annotation generated by this class. The annotation contains following information:
    • Model ID
    • Hostname
    • Date
    • XitoSBML version and credit
    Date Created: Oct 3, 2015
    Author:
    Kaito Ii <ii@fun.bio.keio.ac.jp>, Akira Funahashi <funa@bio.keio.ac.jp>
